{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Official Soundtrack release of 8-Bit Adventures 2 <strong>contains 91 songs - over 4 hours of music in total!</strong> Composed entirely by Sebastian Cruz (also known as Carfonu), this exciting and emotional JRPG soundtrack takes inspiration from 80s and 90s genre classics, while also creating a distinct sound that's all its own.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>In addition to the Original Soundtrack</strong> (82 chiptune songs composed with authentic, NES-accurate tools), <strong>this release exclusively features 9 orchestrated tracks.</strong> These arrangements comprise the Composer's Selection, and re-imagine the 8-bit themes in new ways. All songs are presented in FLAC format, for a high quality listening experience.<br><br>The soundtrack has been recently updated to feature 6 brand new tracks connected to the game's newly released Free DLC!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281060/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738379144","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281060/page.bg.jpg?t=1738379144","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281060/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738379144","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281060/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738379144","categories":[{"description":"Additional High-Quality Audio","id":50}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Official Soundtrack release of 8-Bit Adventures 2 <strong>contains 91 songs - over 4 hours of music in total!</strong> Composed entirely by Sebastian Cruz (also known as Carfonu), this exciting and emotional JRPG soundtrack takes inspiration from 80s and 90s genre classics, while also creating a distinct sound that's all its own.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb